      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a strong shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and some light surface scratches consistent with normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with all electronics and climate controls functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it drives smoothly with no known issues, making it a reliable and attractive option for its next owner.",
