    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only minor signs of wear consistent with regular use. The exterior paint still shines, though you may find a few small scratches or stone chips upon close inspection. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner.",
